<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> LOCATION OF THE SPACE FOR MOUNTING AND THE FIXING OF PLATES </inglise>
<eesti> PAIGALDUSKOHA ASUKOHT JA M&Auml;RGI KINNITAMINE </eesti>
<inglise> The space for mounting shall be such that after correct fixing, the plates shall have the following characteristics: </inglise>
<eesti> Paigalduskoht peab olema selline, et p&auml;rast korrektset kinnitamist oleksid m&auml;rgil j&auml;rgmised karakteristikud: </eesti>
<inglise> 2.1. </inglise>
<eesti> 2.1. </eesti>
<inglise> Position of the plate in relation to the longitudinal axis of the vehicle </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;rgi asukoht s&otilde;iduki pikitelje suhtes </eesti>
<inglise> The centre point of the plate may not be situated to the right of the longitudinal plane of symmetry of the vehicle. </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;rgi keskkoht ei tohi paikneda s&otilde;iduki pikis&uuml;mmeetriatasandi suhtes paremal. </eesti>
<inglise> The left-hand edge of the plate may not be situated to the left of the vertical plane which is parallel to the longitudinal plane of symmetry and touches the extreme outer edge of the vehicle. </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;rgi vasakpoolne serv ei tohi paikneda vasakul pool vertikaaltasandist, mis on paralleelne pikis&uuml;mmetriateljega ja puudutab s&otilde;iduki k&otilde;ige v&auml;lisemat serva. </eesti>
<inglise> 2.2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2.2. </eesti>
<inglise> Position of the plate in relation to the longitudinal plane of symmetry of the vehicle </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;rgi asukoht s&otilde;iduki pikis&uuml;mmeetriatasandi suhtes </eesti>
<inglise> The plate shall be perpendicular, or practically perpendicular, to the longitudinal plane of symmetry of the vehicle. </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;rk on risti v&otilde;i osaliselt risti s&otilde;iduki pikis&uuml;mmeetriatasandi suhtes. </eesti>
<inglise> 2.3. </inglise>
<eesti> 2.3. </eesti>
<inglise> Position of the plate in relation to the vertical plane </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;rgi asukoht s&otilde;iduki vertikaaltasandi suhtes </eesti>
<inglise> The plate shall be vertical subject to a tolerance of 5&deg;. </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;rk on vertikaalselt, lubatud h&auml;lve on 5&deg;. </eesti>
<inglise> Where the shape of the vehicle so requires, however, it may be inclined to the vertical: </inglise>
<eesti> S&otilde;iduki kujust tulenevalt v&otilde;ib see olla vertikaalsuunas kallutatud: </eesti>
<inglise> 2.3.1. at not more than 30&deg; when the surface bearing the registration number faces upwards, provided that the height of the upper edge of the plate is not more than 1.20 metres from the ground; </inglise>
<eesti> 2.3.1. mitte &uuml;le 30&deg;, kui pind, millele registreerimism&auml;rk on kinnitatud, on kallutatud &uuml;lespoole, tingimusel et m&auml;rgi &uuml;lemine serv ei ole maapinnast k&otilde;rgemal kui 1,2 meetrit; </eesti>
<inglise> 2.3.2. at not more than 15&deg; when the surface bearing the registration number faces downwards, provided that the height of the upper edge of the plate is more than 1.20 metres from the ground. </inglise>
<eesti> 2.3.2. mitte &uuml;le 15&deg;, kui pind, millele registreerimism&auml;rk on kinnitatud, on kallutatud allapoole, tingimusel et m&auml;rgi &uuml;lemine serv ei ole maapinnast k&otilde;rgemal kui 1,2 meetrit. </eesti>
<inglise> 2.4. </inglise>
<eesti> 2.4. </eesti>
<inglise> Height of the plate from the ground </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;rgi k&otilde;rgus maapinnast </eesti>
<inglise> The height of the lower edge of the plate from the ground shall not be less than 0.30 metres; the height of the upper edge of the plate from the ground shall not be more than 1.20 metres. </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;rgi alumise serva k&otilde;rgus maapinnast ei ole alla 0,3 meetri; m&auml;rgi &uuml;lemise serva k&otilde;rgus maapinnast ei ole &uuml;le 1,2 meetri. </eesti>
<inglise> However, where it is impossible in practice to comply with this latter provision, the height may exceed 1.20 metres but it must then be as close to that limit as the constructional characteristics of the vehicle allow and must in no case exceed 2 metres. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui tegelikkuses ei ole v&otilde;imalik viimast s&auml;tet t&auml;ita, v&otilde;ib k&otilde;rgus &uuml;letada 1,2 meetrit, kuid see peab siiski olema nii l&auml;hedal sellele m&otilde;&otilde;dule, kui s&otilde;iduki ehituslikud karakteristikud seda v&otilde;imaldavad, ning mingil juhul ei tohi see &uuml;letada 2 meetrit. </eesti>
<inglise> 2.5. </inglise>
<eesti> 2.5. </eesti>
<inglise> Geometrical requirements regarding visibility </inglise>
<eesti> Geomeetrilised n&otilde;uded seoses n&auml;htavusega </eesti>
<inglise> The plate shall be visible in the whole space included within the following four planes, viz: the two vertical planes touching the two lateral edges of the plate and forming an angle measured outwards of 30&deg; with the longitudinal median of the vehicle; the plane touching the upper edge of the plate and forming an angle measured upwards of 15&deg; with the horizontal; the horizontal plane through the lower edge of the plate (however, if the height of the upper edge of the plate from the ground is greater than 1.20 metres, this latter plane shall form an angle measured downwards of 15&deg; with the horizontal). </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;rk peab olema kogu ulatuses n&auml;htav neljalt j&auml;rgmiselt tasandilt: kaks vertikaaltasandit, mis puudutavad m&auml;rgi kahte k&uuml;lgserva ja moodustavad s&otilde;iduki pikikesktasandiga m&auml;rgi k&uuml;lgservas 30&deg; nurga; tasand, mis puudutab m&auml;rgi &uuml;lemist serva ja moodustab horisontaaltasandiga m&auml;rgi &uuml;lemises servas 15&deg; nurga; horisontaaltasand l&auml;bi m&auml;rgi alumise serva (kuid kui m&auml;rgi &uuml;lemise serva k&otilde;rgus maapinnast on &uuml;le 1,2 meetri, moodustab see viimane tasand horisontaaltasapinnaga m&auml;rgi alumises servas 15&deg; nurga). </eesti>
<inglise> 2.6. </inglise>
<eesti> 2.6. </eesti>
<inglise> Determination of the height of the plate from the ground </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;rgi k&otilde;rguse m&auml;&auml;ramine maapinnast </eesti>
<inglise> The heights given in 2.3, 2.4 and 2.5 shall be measured with the vehicle unladen. </inglise>
<eesti> Punktides 2.3, 2.4 ja 2.5 esitatud k&otilde;rgused m&otilde;&otilde;detakse koormata s&otilde;idukil. </eesti>
 